page.title: 18A Cottage and its Contents 2
page.content: {Kitchen -}round table, 4 chairs, Welsh dresser, electric cooker, microwave cooker, automatic washing machine, refrigerator, food processor, electric toaster, electric kettle, coffee maker, radio/cassette player, telephone, cupboards, double draining boards (stainless steel) and sink,2 stools, waste bin, coal hods, broom cupboard with mops, buckets etc., vacuum cleaner, fish tank, mirror,pots and pans,shopping trolley, carpet sweeper, radiator, vinyl floor covering, 2 rugs. {Child's Bedroom}- Bunk Beds, Radiator, Chest of Drawers (Clothes), Chest of Drawers (Toys), 2 Bookcases, Toy Cupboard, Fitted Carpet, Bedside Mat, Playmat, Pin Board.
